OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will stay dry with good
OL,6,Fprolonged sunny spells. After a frosty
OL,7,Fstart it will feel cooler than recent
OL,8,Fdays. Cloudier in the west with
OL,9,Fincreasingly strong south to southwest
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry with often clear
OL,13,Fskies at first, but cloud gradually
OL,14,Fspreading in from the west. Strong
OL,15,Fsouth to southwest winds developing,
OL,16,Fcoastal gales in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
