OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FIt will remain dry for most
OL,6,Fon Saturday. Feeling mild with some
OL,7,Fbright spells or hazy sunshine in the
OL,8,Feast. Windy and cloudy in the west
OL,9,Fwith occasional rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,12,Fcloud and bright spells with
OL,13,Foccasional rain in the east on Sunday
OL,14,Fand Monday, cloudy with more
OL,15,Fpersistent rain in the west. Becoming
OL,16,Fwindier Tuesday as rain spreads east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
